title: Firefox crashes when i try to export logins
content:
Hi,

I've been having problems with my computer lately and several programs crash at random intervals, including firefox. This is why im backing up information before doing a factory reset. One of the things i need to back up are my logins, but every time i try to export them firefox crashes. Are there any other alternatives for backing up my logins?
